contract.name: HorseFarm
abi: event Lease(address indexed owner, address indexed signer, uint256 indexed horseId, string nonce)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
event Withdraw(address indexed owner, address indexed signer, uint256 indexed horseId, string nonce)
function lease(tuple(address owner, uint256 horseId, uint256 blockExpired, string nonce, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s) data)
function leaseData(string) view returns (address owner, uint256 horseId, uint256 blockExpired)
function onERC721Received(address, address, uint256, bytes) returns (bytes4)
function withdraw(tuple(address owner, uint256 horseId, uint256 blockExpired, string nonce, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s) data)
function withdrawData(string) view returns (address owner, uint256 horseId, uint256 blockExpired)
